snippet.title: Matthew Trayling
snippet.description:
Matthew Trayling is a Melbourne based musician currently recording various styles of music and tracks in his home studio. At 52 years of age, it is only in the last 3 years he has become active again after more than a 20 year lull..
His channel originally developed to promote not only his own music, but his incredibly talented Mother - Natalie Trayling
Natalie in Matthew's own words is "arguably the best ‘unknown’ composer in the world today”

As you go through his uploads it it quite obvious that Natalie is gaining world wide recognition not just as a street performer, but as a "profound musical genius", a description she rightly deserves, and to add...is agreed with by many.
Information on Natalie -

http://www.theage.com.au/national/virtuoso-ha

http://www.abc.net.au/news/2013-11-01/pianist-bring

http://www.inquisitr.com/1557578/natalie-trayling-piano-musician/

And Matthew Trayling -

https://soundcloud.com/matting-1
